Subject: Re: [T2] kill switch placement ?

select the wire going to the starter solenoid.  make sure you route it 
in such a way that some one trying to hotwire doesnt spot it.  Buses and 
vanagons are very easy to hotwire.  Found that out when i made a remote 
start switch for mine.
